Effect of Telehealth Extended Care for Maintenance of Weight Loss in Rural US 
Communities: A Randomized Clinical Trial.

Perri MG(1), Shankar MN(1), Daniels MJ(2), Durning PE(1), Ross KM(1), Limacher 
MC(3), Janicke DM(1), Martin AD(4), Dhara K(2), Bobroff LB(5), Radcliff TA(6), 
